                        <name role="metadata">MCGREGOR, Gregor</name>
                        <name role="display">Senator McGREGOR</name>
                    </talker>
                    <para>. -  I have been asked a direct question as to the intentions of the Opposition in the Senate in connexion with the future. When manna came down from heaven it was not supposed to be safe to take more than one day&#39;s supply. &#34; Sufficient for the day is the evil thereof.&#34; </para>
                </talk.start>
